    <item>
      <title>欧盟金融部长对小型集团持开放态度 推动建立资本联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/eu-financial-chief-open-to-small-blocs-in-push-for-capital-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟金融服务主管表示，欧盟可能考虑推进“自愿联盟”，而不必等待所有 27 个成员国就资本市场联盟达成一致，以打破其十年计划的僵局，并填补近万亿欧元的投资缺口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/eu-financial-chief-open-to-small-blocs-in-push-for-capital-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国总理舒尔茨和默茨将移民问题带到议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/germany-s-scholz-and-merz-take-migration-battle-to-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离德国联邦选举不到四周时间，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨和民调领先的保守派挑战者弗里德里希·梅尔茨将就如何打击非法移民展开激烈争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/germany-s-scholz-and-merz-take-migration-battle-to-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示瑞士将投票否决严格的排放限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/swiss-set-to-reject-strict-emission-curbs-in-vote-polls-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士选民将否决绿党青年团提出的一套严格的气候规则，因为大多数民众认为经济成本太高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/swiss-set-to-reject-strict-emission-curbs-in-vote-polls-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国高铁有望 2030 年通车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/thai-high-speed-rail-linking-bangkok-to-china-eyes-2030-opening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国预计将于 2030 年完成其首条经老挝连接中国的高铁网络，这一长期推迟的项目被官员们誉为进一步发展两国双边关系和贸易的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/thai-high-speed-rail-linking-bangkok-to-china-eyes-2030-opening</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 04:27:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
